Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:18.61,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}The brilliant glow of this sky, does it carry right into your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.88,0:00:28.58,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,1600)\3c&H141414&}The melody you heard in your dream, it plays like the silence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.58,0:00:33.68,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Even if your hands are still far from that dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.68,0:00:38.65,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Come now and remember that kindly voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.65,0:00:51.26,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(50,200)\3c&H141414&}Someone was there singing for you, singing those chords of happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:01:00.96,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Sound of the sky, echo on high, break through that overwhelming sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:05.80,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Everything that shines in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.80,0:01:11.47,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,400)\3c&H141414&}Is part of the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:20.77,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,200)\3c&H141414&}Even your tears can't leave you here to stay forever
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.77,0:01:33.27,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,4000)\3c&H141414&}In this light pouring down onto you, play tomorrow's song
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:01.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:09.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.46,0:02:23.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's the way we'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:24.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:26.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,As for where we condu-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:29.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading out, Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.98,0:02:33.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.73,0:02:36.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Already planning to use your first paycheck?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:37.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.84,0:02:39.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sending some home,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.37,0:02:43.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and I thought I'd send some souvenirs back, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:44.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A little treat for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:46.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:51.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The first month was just training so you didn't get anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:52.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Excited, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:54.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:03:00.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that we were usually paid late, and then in military scrip.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:03.43,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are. Good work this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:07.91,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:13.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I would get real money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:17.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you do. Why do you think we have our other busine-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.31,0:03:24.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, um... Er... There's a flea market in town today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:25.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your first time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.75,0:03:27.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Your first paycheck and your first day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.34,0:03:30.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A first time for everything and right on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:34.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about your day job and take a good look at everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:35.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:41.10,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&00&}Kanata's Day Off - Hair Ties
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.35,0:03:45.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going then!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:56.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to say anything suspicious around Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:57.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But just think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:04:04.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting paid in the middle of nowhere and without even a late supply shipment?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:13.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And... she actually believed you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:16.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She accepts what she gets. That's Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:17.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:22.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you two. You found out where we got the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:24.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And how.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:30.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:34.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Why don't we forget about our day jobs, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:43.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,476)}It's got character.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:44.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:47.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's just one fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:49.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The price isn't going any lower.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:56.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I didn't notice you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:11.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:14.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We haven't run into any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:17.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've run into some.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:21.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got an idea to take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:22.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:25.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me more about this idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:32.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This one is nice too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:54.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the fine shopkeeper. You selling these?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:04.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you like our goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.20,0:06:05.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:11.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But, there's just one fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:13.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:18.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got this many. It would take some work and a few connections to sell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:22.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And we don't have the resources for that, you get what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:23.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:26.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a no-discount policy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:28.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The price is part of the taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:32.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't ask you to lower the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just take them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.09,0:06:38.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:46.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and shoot. If you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:49.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause before you can,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:52.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,this gun in my hand would blow your head clean off, just like your hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:54.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.32,0:06:58.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not very smart, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:06.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what you get for taking me lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:09.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:42.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I warned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:48.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Punk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:51.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You one of their friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:57.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:06.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The car!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:08.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:11.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:12.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But the souvenirs for the Don?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:15.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Worthless if we're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:16.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.09,0:08:18.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No one said anything about maniacs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:22.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're never coming back again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:27.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:29.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.83,0:08:33.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can get up now, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:38.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I was scared for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:40.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like we fooled them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.59,0:08:43.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:49.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. If the mob got a foothold here, our business would go kaput.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:53.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little give-and-take.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:54.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.19,0:08:58.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be giving us our fee for this little play.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:02.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my. Mikhail, you do have a sense of humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:05.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:07.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.62,0:09:10.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we talk business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:13.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't I take those?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:17.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bust their car there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:20.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:22.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:24.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:27.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like someone busted their car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:33.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And there were some goods that they bought at the flea market.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:38.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't I say I bought those and we split the profits?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:43.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems we've reached an agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:44.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.24,0:09:49.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So the play's finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:52.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was quite a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:53.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What was?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:57.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You were completely in character, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.33,0:10:02.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone discovered that we're distilling this, we'd have more than a court-martial on our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:05.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct violations of the anti-trust laws and tax laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.11,0:10:08.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,At worst, charges of treason.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:12.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. We picked up this business after the ones before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:15.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And Rio's never been against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:17.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a bit surprised too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:27.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was surprised myself at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:29.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This calvados
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:30.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,was my mother's favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:33.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And it was made here at the fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:42.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe your mother was responsible for your station here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.94,0:10:51.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an3}Sound of the Skies
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:55.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an1}Sound of the Skies
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:03.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.57,0:11:12.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Yumina!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:15.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:18.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wonderful, Seiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:26.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:30.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is their first visit to the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:33.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The priest will be there today. So, just for today...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:34.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:41.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't start causing her problems now. At least let her do your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:43.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I won't let her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:47.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? You always tell me to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.59,0:11:49.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:56.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that, Mishio.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:00.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:08.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,¥10.25.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:13.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Look where you're going, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:16.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I didn't notice you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:21.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, these bumpkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:21.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:24.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they've heard about our business.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:30.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:31.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:36.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But Miss Naomi, tell me, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:41.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've had enough money in my purse to buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:43.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If I ask for it, I could just buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:49.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What if someone came in and wanted to buy that dolphin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:53.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone say they wanted to buy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:55.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, just a hypothetical question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.81,0:13:00.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... I would...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:05.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I would tell them that dolphins were really scary people-eating animals and make sure they didn't buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:09.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You're a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.19,0:13:12.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and that dolphin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:16.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep it until you say you don't want it anymore, so relax and worry all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:21.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll buy everyone's souvenirs first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:28.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Dad, Mom, Grandpa, Grandma,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:33.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma and Grandpa Warren, Great-grandma,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:35.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and Grandma Nanae next door!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:40.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:42.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's so much stuff to choose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.56,0:13:43.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:46.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:50.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mishio?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.55,0:13:53.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you out shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.03,0:13:56.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like she's looking for a box.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:13:57.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A box?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:14:00.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this. Did you see one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:04.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:10.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I help you look for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.73,0:14:12.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:16.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to buy souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:20.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking for something wonderful to send to my family back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.78,0:14:23.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not in a hurry-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:23.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:35.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why Mishio said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:42.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:44.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's quite nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:47.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This one is nice too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:52.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Yumina?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:55.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Miss Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.84,0:14:57.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Mishio?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:02.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A box?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:04.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. She said it was important.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:07.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:13.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When her mother died, all of her family's belonging's were taken from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:19.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's supposed to be a memento that her mother left her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:24.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}When she heard about the flea market, she thought she might find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.06,0:15:29.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I said something wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:33.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I received my first paycheck yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:36.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And I told her I was sending presents back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:38.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:41.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:44.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We are trying to be her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:49.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If she were still jealous of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.83,0:15:53.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,then it's because I'm not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:11.04,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama, which is more important to you, me or your treasure box?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.93,0:16:13.11,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.34,0:16:19.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.37,0:16:27.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:38.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:47.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,These are Treize's famous firecrackers! They'll crack like thunder! How about 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:57.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister... Sister Yumina...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:16:59.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.23,0:17:00.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:08.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The car!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:17.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm not Yumina.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:26.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister! Sister Yumina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.05,0:17:30.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.\NKeep up the good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:35.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:36.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:41.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:47.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that car... yours, Miss Naomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:50.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you two did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:55.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry! There's ¥150 in here, so
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:17:56.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:59.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.09,0:18:05.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can keep that. I already got my payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:11.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Naomi! That box!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:19.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,These ideographs mean "beautiful rice stalk".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.92,0:18:26.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Carve them into her seal and I assure you she will have a life as full of happiness as a bountiful field of rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.93,0:18:27.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:32.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Miho, aren't you so happy to receive such a great fortune?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:40.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find Mishio?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:47.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I had done everything to be her family,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.88,0:18:50.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm still not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:54.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you are trying hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.98,0:19:00.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.28,0:19:07.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful! You found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Take good care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:12.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an irreplaceable memento from your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.93,0:19:13.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.27,0:19:16.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This box...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:19.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:32.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio was taken in by the church after she lost her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:38.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Her father was sent to the front lines and never returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:40.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And her mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:46.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio's family lived on the Eastern region of Vingt-et-Un
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:48.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:52.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the town stricken by the Invisible Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:59.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When they arrived here in Seize, her mother was already showing symptoms, and soon after...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.79,0:20:04.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:08.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She said, "Sorry I can't do your hair anymore."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:16.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And she told me... to have the person who cares about me most tie my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:20.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tie it, Yumina?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:28.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Man lives on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.02,0:20:34.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after being separated from those we love and suffer as though dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:40.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We still live on. We can live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:44.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That strength is our sorrow. Our love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.84,0:20:50.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.73,0:20:51.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.69,0:20:53.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.97,0:21:07.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's already in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.88,0:21:09.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'll go soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.63,0:21:15.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You had a long day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:19.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I didn't really want to wash my hair,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:21.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but things happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:26.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Oh! Oh! Let me dry your hair for you, Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.74,0:21:29.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:36.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So you didn't buy the dolphin?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:39.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that would be your little treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.56,0:21:45.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio, do you believe in destiny?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.04,0:21:47.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:53.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, something that felt like it happened today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.46,0:21:56.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That was enough of a treat for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.07,0:22:05.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe in it. I don't like the idea that anything's already decided for you before you even get a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.10,0:22:09.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I do believe
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.28,0:22:13.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,that one small thing someone does
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.78,0:22:15.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,can work its way up and up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.75,0:22:19.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and change someone's life in an amazing way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.59,0:22:26.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's destiny,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:30.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,then maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.20,0:22:31.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.32,0:22:39.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,D-flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:49.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Rio had a wonderful day today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.47,0:22:58.03,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - put these feelings together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.39,0:23:01.50,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}And sing of how important they are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.68,0:23:19.26,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I was so happy that I cried
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.44,0:23:25.35,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It hurt so bad that I laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.44,0:23:34.13,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But that all just goes to show that I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.36,0:23:38.73,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,800)}Let's just walk it slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.76,0:23:40.36,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}Everybody singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.45,0:23:44.70,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Just tell me a bit of what you think
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.78,0:23:45.91,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}You're just my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.91,0:23:51.75,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - even though they might waver
Dialogue: 1,0:23:49.34,0:23:51.75,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8\3c&HE5A9EA&}I know, you know, little happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.93,0:23:57.72,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I want us to echo on forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.93,0:23:57.72,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8\3c&HE5A9EA&}Can you hear my precious note?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.09,0:24:03.72,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}All these words that there are can't even describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.98,0:24:09.56,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.88,0:24:14.51,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}Can you hear it? Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.81,0:24:26.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(320,180)\c&H020202&\bord0}Next time: Chirping Crickets - Floating Lights on the River
